WEBVTT

00:00:06.679 --> 00:00:08.000
The day Bro Mao disappeared,

00:00:08.640 --> 00:00:09.919
Luo Xiao was the one who took him away.

00:00:10.759 --> 00:00:11.439
Where Bro Mao was hiding,

00:00:11.439 --> 00:00:12.720
only Luo Xiao knew.

00:00:13.679 --> 00:00:15.080
He gave me an address,

00:00:15.279 --> 00:00:16.640
said Bro Mao was hiding there.

00:00:18.440 --> 00:00:19.600
Only later did I realize

00:00:20.480 --> 00:00:22.239
it was a trap they set for me.

00:00:25.320 --> 00:00:26.640
After Bro Mao disappeared,

00:00:27.320 --> 00:00:29.160
Luo Xiao suddenly got involved out of nowhere,

00:00:29.239 --> 00:00:30.079
claiming that

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:33.200
Bro Mao signed a contract with him.

00:00:34.159 --> 00:00:35.280
What a joke.

00:00:35.880 --> 00:00:36.840
We all know

00:00:37.799 --> 00:00:39.920
Bro Mao was uneducated, he couldn't read.

00:00:40.280 --> 00:00:42.359
How could he even sign a real contract?

00:00:43.159 --> 00:00:45.479
And with no news from him,

00:00:46.079 --> 00:00:47.320
I suspected back then

00:00:48.799 --> 00:00:51.159
that Luo Xiao might've killed Bro Mao.

00:01:00.119 --> 00:01:01.079
He's lying.

00:01:01.759 --> 00:01:02.840
This is slander.

00:01:03.640 --> 00:01:04.599
He's framing me.

00:01:05.079 --> 00:01:05.879
He's using me

00:01:05.879 --> 00:01:07.560
to get a lighter sentence for himself.

00:01:08.040 --> 00:01:09.400
The day you're talking about,

00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:11.280
I was just there to request leave.

00:01:12.120 --> 00:01:14.560
I brought some files over to Fengmao.

00:01:16.040 --> 00:01:17.400
My daughter was waiting in the car.

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:18.920
On my way out,

00:01:19.359 --> 00:01:21.480
I ran into my brother-in-law, Zhang Heng.

00:01:22.239 --> 00:01:23.319
We chatted for quite a while.

00:01:24.400 --> 00:01:25.519
He can vouch for me.

00:01:30.920 --> 00:01:33.000
Let's go through that day again.

00:01:33.280 --> 00:01:34.480
That day, you had your daughter with you,

00:01:34.640 --> 00:01:35.840
driving along Wan'an East Road

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:37.959
heading out of the city for a while.

00:01:38.280 --> 00:01:40.400
Suddenly you remembered to deliver files,

00:01:40.560 --> 00:01:42.319
which just happened to be in the car.

00:01:42.599 --> 00:01:44.799
So you drove right back to Fengmao.

00:01:45.079 --> 00:01:46.200
And coincidentally, Chen Yongjiang

00:01:46.359 --> 00:01:47.680
vanished from that day onward.

00:01:48.159 --> 00:01:49.879
Then Shi Qijun, replacing Chen Yongjiang,

00:01:49.879 --> 00:01:51.239
kept contacting you frequently.

00:01:51.480 --> 00:01:53.280
Huang Qiuping came to you for help with

00:01:53.359 --> 00:01:54.719
her marital assets.

00:01:55.200 --> 00:01:56.519
Then Min Shengquan kidnapped you both

00:01:56.519 --> 00:01:58.280
and took you to your auto repair shop.

00:02:04.159 --> 00:02:05.640
One coincidence is understandable.

00:02:07.040 --> 00:02:08.759
But every single time?

00:02:09.360 --> 00:02:10.080
Luo Xiao,

00:02:11.159 --> 00:02:12.520
we're trying to help you.

00:02:53.680 --> 00:02:54.759
Come home for dinner.

00:02:57.719 --> 00:02:59.000
Come home for dinner.

00:03:01.719 --> 00:03:03.319
I said, it's time to come home and eat.

00:03:05.240 --> 00:03:06.120
What are you doing here?

00:03:10.000 --> 00:03:11.800
A grown man always at the internet cafe.

00:03:12.400 --> 00:03:13.039
Ping.

00:03:13.159 --> 00:03:14.439
I... I was just...

00:03:14.919 --> 00:03:16.240
just zoning out here for a bit.

00:03:16.240 --> 00:03:17.719
I mean, I already paid for the time.

00:03:17.800 --> 00:03:18.719
I really...

00:03:26.639 --> 00:03:27.840
Is something bothering you?

00:03:29.240 --> 00:03:31.000
Same old stuff, every day.

00:03:32.400 --> 00:03:33.439
Is it because of my brother-in-law?

00:03:39.080 --> 00:03:40.039
Right now,

00:03:41.400 --> 00:03:42.599
who am I?

00:03:43.520 --> 00:03:44.120
Who are you?

00:03:44.120 --> 00:03:45.719
You're Zhang Heng. Who else?

00:03:49.159 --> 00:03:50.800
Am I Zhang Heng the brother-in-law,

00:03:51.759 --> 00:03:53.120
or Zhang Heng the cop?

00:04:07.479 --> 00:04:09.719
Nobody wants a criminal brother-in-law.

00:04:10.280 --> 00:04:10.960
But regardless of whether

00:04:10.960 --> 00:04:12.360
this has anything to do with him,

00:04:12.800 --> 00:04:14.120
don't you still have to

00:04:14.120 --> 00:04:15.080
get to the bottom of this case?

00:04:20.560 --> 00:04:21.920
You're here beating yourself up.

00:04:22.399 --> 00:04:23.519
No matter the reason,

00:04:24.680 --> 00:04:26.920
family ties can't be what holds you back.

00:04:34.480 --> 00:04:36.639
You're the best, honey.

00:04:39.079 --> 00:04:39.839
Let's go home.

00:04:40.519 --> 00:04:41.560
I've got some soup simmering for you.

00:04:41.600 --> 00:04:42.279
Okay.

00:04:43.199 --> 00:04:44.920
To build your strength back up.

00:04:46.439 --> 00:04:47.040
Let's go.

00:04:50.839 --> 00:04:52.560
Or I could play a bit longer.

00:04:52.639 --> 00:04:53.399
Home. Now.

00:04:57.480 --> 00:04:58.120
Chief Wang.

00:04:58.759 --> 00:05:00.079
The Min Shengquan case

00:05:00.360 --> 00:05:01.959
has now implicated Luo Xiao.

00:05:02.720 --> 00:05:04.439
Given he's my brother-in-law,

00:05:05.000 --> 00:05:06.759
to ensure the evidence's legal validity

00:05:06.879 --> 00:05:08.199
and the fairness of the investigation,

00:05:08.639 --> 00:05:10.199
I'm formally requesting the bureau

00:05:10.519 --> 00:05:12.439
to let me withdraw from the investigation.

00:05:17.079 --> 00:05:18.439
I understand your concerns.

00:05:19.759 --> 00:05:21.120
But this case

00:05:21.560 --> 00:05:23.240
has reached a critical point.

00:05:23.720 --> 00:05:25.759
The leads span a wide scope,

00:05:26.480 --> 00:05:27.639
and much of the evidence

00:05:28.120 --> 00:05:30.079
is best known by you and your team.

00:05:30.720 --> 00:05:34.160
So, you'll stay in charge of this case.

00:05:34.639 --> 00:05:36.759
But investigate by the book,

00:05:37.199 --> 00:05:38.160
and enforce with reason.

00:05:38.480 --> 00:05:40.079
Mind your methods.

00:05:40.360 --> 00:05:41.120
Understood?

00:05:43.439 --> 00:05:44.160
Understood.

00:05:46.439 --> 00:05:47.240
Come on out.

00:05:51.800 --> 00:05:52.439
Let's go.

00:06:08.079 --> 00:06:08.879
Godfather.

00:06:10.360 --> 00:06:11.600
Luo Xiao and Min Shengquan

00:06:11.839 --> 00:06:13.040
have been taken in by the police.

00:06:13.680 --> 00:06:15.560
Huang Qiuping was at the auto shop,

00:06:15.800 --> 00:06:17.079
and Shengquan stabbed her to death.

00:06:21.959 --> 00:06:23.160
Have Attorney Bai come over.

00:06:23.560 --> 00:06:24.199
Okay.

00:06:34.839 --> 00:06:35.600
You guys keep looking.

00:06:36.000 --> 00:06:37.519
I... I need to hit the restroom.

00:06:45.519 --> 00:06:46.279
Boss.

00:06:47.040 --> 00:06:49.319
We tracked Luo Xiao's vehicle movements.

00:06:49.639 --> 00:06:51.240
Only this road has no data.

00:06:53.360 --> 00:06:54.680
But on this road,

00:06:55.199 --> 00:06:56.399
there's just a cemetery.

00:06:58.360 --> 00:06:59.879
No surveillance along this whole route.

00:07:00.720 --> 00:07:01.759
None at the cemetery either?

00:07:01.839 --> 00:07:02.680
Let me check.

00:07:06.199 --> 00:07:06.879
Nope.

00:07:08.319 --> 00:07:08.959
Boss.

00:07:10.360 --> 00:07:11.680
Why would Luo Xiao go to a cemetery?

00:07:17.600 --> 00:07:18.800
Captain Zhang, the lawyer's here.

00:07:18.920 --> 00:07:19.800
He wants to see Min Shengquan.

00:07:33.600 --> 00:07:35.000
What's going on?

00:07:35.560 --> 00:07:37.480
He recanted right after seeing his lawyer?

00:07:37.600 --> 00:07:38.439
Contact the detention center now.

00:07:38.439 --> 00:07:39.519
We're interrogating Min Shengquan again.

00:07:39.560 --> 00:07:40.079
Got it.

00:07:41.160 --> 00:07:42.720
I forgot the exact details.

00:07:43.439 --> 00:07:45.639
Anyway, Bro Mao ran off.

00:07:45.759 --> 00:07:46.759
I sent men to find him.

00:07:47.399 --> 00:07:48.480
Once they found him,

00:07:49.639 --> 00:07:50.839
I killed him outright.

00:07:50.920 --> 00:07:51.879
Chopped him up.

00:07:53.399 --> 00:07:55.439
Later, his wife suspected me.

00:07:55.639 --> 00:07:56.680
She even threatened me.

00:07:57.839 --> 00:07:59.480
So I killed her too.

00:08:01.279 --> 00:08:03.439
Luo Xiao had bad luck running into it.

00:08:04.199 --> 00:08:05.480
I figured

00:08:06.360 --> 00:08:08.639
I'd grab cash from his garage and split.

00:08:08.879 --> 00:08:09.839
Then you guys showed up.

00:08:13.199 --> 00:08:14.319
All this time,

00:08:15.480 --> 00:08:18.160
you wired Fengmao for various purposes.

00:08:18.879 --> 00:08:20.600
Partnership fees, promotion fees,

00:08:20.720 --> 00:08:21.879
repayments, loans.

00:08:22.839 --> 00:08:24.720
Why exactly did you kill Chen Yongjiang?

00:08:29.079 --> 00:08:30.240
In my own name,

00:08:30.680 --> 00:08:32.480
I borrowed a huge sum from him.

00:08:32.879 --> 00:08:34.759
If he's dead, I don't have to pay it back.

00:08:36.039 --> 00:08:37.480
But Chen Yongjiang already ran away.

00:08:37.960 --> 00:08:39.200
Wasn't that overkill?

00:08:40.279 --> 00:08:41.559
But he had underlings.

00:08:42.360 --> 00:08:44.440
His guys could come collect from me.

00:08:45.480 --> 00:08:47.000
So I forged some documents,

00:08:47.440 --> 00:08:49.639
making Fengmao's people answer to me.

00:08:50.039 --> 00:08:51.200
I don't owe a thing.

00:08:51.320 --> 00:08:53.159
The whole Fengmao Company is mine.

00:08:54.039 --> 00:08:55.080
Then why did you say at first

00:08:55.080 --> 00:08:56.080
that Luo Xiao was the killer,

00:08:56.159 --> 00:08:57.240
and now you're recanting?

00:08:58.759 --> 00:08:59.879
Have you ever killed anyone?

00:09:00.879 --> 00:09:02.080
Have you ever been arrested?

00:09:02.480 --> 00:09:04.519
Just tell the truth.

00:09:04.679 --> 00:09:05.799
Watch your attitude!

00:09:09.639 --> 00:09:12.240
Look, I've done so much,

00:09:13.039 --> 00:09:14.519
you'd catch me sooner or later.

00:09:15.799 --> 00:09:16.960
Huang Qiuping is dead too.

00:09:18.679 --> 00:09:20.240
I might as well come clean for leniency,

00:09:21.080 --> 00:09:22.279
shoot for a suspended death sentence.

00:09:22.840 --> 00:09:24.039
Behave well,

00:09:24.320 --> 00:09:25.879
and I get a few more years to live.

00:09:28.080 --> 00:09:29.759
You chopped up Chen Yongjiang.

00:09:30.200 --> 00:09:31.120
Then why did you fall for

00:09:31.120 --> 00:09:32.600
the fake address Luo Xiao gave you

00:09:32.720 --> 00:09:34.000
and go throw a Molotov?

00:09:34.600 --> 00:09:36.240
To kill someone you'd already killed?

00:09:41.639 --> 00:09:42.519
Min Shengquan.

00:09:44.120 --> 00:09:45.320
Here's the thing.

00:09:48.799 --> 00:09:50.000
Between us,

00:09:50.720 --> 00:09:53.320
there's actually a lot we can talk about,

00:09:53.440 --> 00:09:54.519
a lot we can discuss.

00:09:54.799 --> 00:09:56.240
You suddenly recanted,

00:09:57.240 --> 00:09:58.879
and we both know why.

00:10:01.720 --> 00:10:02.879
What we can do

00:10:03.559 --> 00:10:05.519
is give you maximum protection,

00:10:06.519 --> 00:10:07.799
especially for your family.

00:10:10.120 --> 00:10:11.279
Can you trust us?

00:10:14.200 --> 00:10:15.399
If you don't believe me,

00:10:15.679 --> 00:10:17.399
go search my room.

00:10:18.279 --> 00:10:19.600
Bro Mao's finger's in there.

00:10:56.200 --> 00:10:57.000
Found it.

00:11:29.120 --> 00:11:30.360
Luo Xiao, come on out.

00:12:22.679 --> 00:12:23.679
When did you get here?

00:12:24.559 --> 00:12:25.960
Just got here, and out you came.

00:12:33.840 --> 00:12:35.840
Things were urgent that day.

00:12:36.159 --> 00:12:37.279
I didn't know who else to call,

00:12:38.120 --> 00:12:39.159
so I called you.

00:12:43.440 --> 00:12:44.320
Don't mention it.

00:12:44.960 --> 00:12:46.639
I'm glad I could help you, brother.

00:12:48.320 --> 00:12:49.279
After we hung up that day,

00:12:49.279 --> 00:12:50.320
something felt off,

00:12:51.240 --> 00:12:52.480
so I went to the garage to wait for you.

00:12:54.440 --> 00:12:55.200
Don't worry, brother.

00:12:58.480 --> 00:13:00.120
Everyone needs a light now and then.

00:13:10.840 --> 00:13:12.240
This cigarette today,

00:13:13.960 --> 00:13:15.240
why's it so damn good?

00:13:17.360 --> 00:13:18.919
If you like 'em, I'll grab a few cartons.

00:13:21.320 --> 00:13:22.120
No,

00:13:24.279 --> 00:13:25.399
it's this one today,

00:13:26.919 --> 00:13:27.799
extra smooth.

00:13:30.240 --> 00:13:31.080
Don't believe me? Try one.

00:13:36.840 --> 00:13:37.759
Don't all cigarettes taste the same?